        <section name="Download"> 
            <p> 
                Here you can download the latest version of Checkstyle Beans plugin.
            </p>
            <p>
                After the installation the plugin should start working immediately.
                When you open a new source file or save an existing one you should
                see the Checkstyle annotations.
            </p>

            <p>
                See the <a href="changes-report.html">Changes Report</a> for
                the complete overview of recent changes.
            </p>
        </section>

